title: A Stranger‚Äôs Last 3 Months to Live
tags: yestheory|seek discomfort|last 24 hours|last 3 months to live|cancer patient|how to deal with cancer|friendship|terminally ill|friend with cancer|rare cancer|yes theory|yes theory stranger
description: When I met Xavier Romero in July of 2019, he'd been given 1 week left to live. He was suffering from a rare form of liver cancer and doctors had given up hope. After hearing his story, I knew I wanted to meet him. Little did I know Xavier would beat all the odds and that we would get to know each other and become brothers. Over three months of getting to know him, he taught me about what it means to fight for your life, to love unconditionally and to appreciate every single breath. He always wanted to start a YouTube channel and I told him that no matter what, his story would be told. He took comfort in that. Here is that story. I know he's here with us. I know he's watching this video and smiling at these beautiful moments we got to spend with each other. I miss him and I know I'll see him again one day. Thank you for watching. It means a lot to me and I know it means a lot to him.Love,MattIf you want to join the Yes Fam Facebook group which is 100,000+ of our most engaged and badass community members, you can apply here: https://www.facebook.com/groups/15653...PERFECT ROYALTY FREE MUSIC FOR YOUTUBE: free 30 day trial here: http://share.epidemicsound.com/wFFbr Musicbed has amazing montage and cinematic music:http://share.mscbd.fm/YesTheoryFor an amazing b-roll and footage library, checkout: http://storyblocks.com/YesTheoryYes Theory Spotify Playlist: https://open.spotify.com/user/t-boogy...Exclusive challenges on Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/yestheory/Who are we? description: The Lakers defeated the Warriors, 125-120. Anthony Davis recorded 27 points, 10 rebounds and 4 assists for the Lakers, while LeBron James added 22 points, 8 rebounds and 11 assists in the victory. description: Hey Guys! Today I am painting on paint palettes. Yep, that's right. It's weird, but also somehow makes completes sense at the same time. I decorated 8 different paint palettes and am using them as decor in my art room. I tried to paint a mix of abstract designs, landscape, cartoony etc. in order to get a good variety for you guys using acrylic paint and posca paint pens. I hope you guys like this new idea! I think I'm kind of obsessed with these custom paint palettes. Don't forget to try it out yourself and tag my on instagram!NEW Phone cases! I asked you guys if you wanted me to have my painted phone case designs re-produced and you did! description: Muahaha! If you're one of those people who insist I buy the optimal tool for every job, you're really gonna hate this one. Today we use a $100 chainsaw and a $30 beam cutter attachment to mill oak into planks. And it works! Then we build a nice little kicker as a proof of concept. Enjoy!Here is Wranglerstar's video on the saw mill: https://youtu.be/kz3g7NB8bC8The mill I used is sold out.
